---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Holiday Homes Downtown Dubai 2026 — From AED 350/night"
  description="Find holiday homes in Downtown Dubai from AED 350/night. Burj Khalifa views. Walking distance to Dubai Mall and Dubai Fountain."
>
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal to-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-green-200 mb-2">📍 Downtown Dubai</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Holiday Homes Downtown Dubai — From AED 350/Night</h1>
  <p class="text-green-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare furnished apartments near Burj Khalifa and Dubai Mall. Fountain views available. Premium location for short stays.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=downtown-homes&type=home" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Find Downtown Holiday Homes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Holiday Homes in Downtown Dubai</h2>
    <p>Downtown Dubai is the city's iconic centre, home to Burj Khalifa, Dubai Mall, Dubai Fountain, and the Dubai Opera. Holiday homes here command a premium, but one-bedroom apartments are available from AED 350/night — still 40–50% cheaper than equivalent 4-star hotel rooms.</p>
    <p>The most popular buildings for short-term stays include The Address Downtown, Burj Vista, and 29 Boulevard. Many apartments offer direct Burj Khalifa or Fountain views. Studios start from AED 280/night in older buildings.</p>
    <p>Downtown is centrally located with metro access (Burj Khalifa/Dubai Mall station) and easy road connections to every part of Dubai. It is the best base for first-time visitors who want to be at the centre of everything.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/holiday-homes" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all holiday home areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
